    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smooth, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you\u2019re just commuting to work or heading out for a fun weekend getaway, this beauty is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it handles!",
